title: Ganwaar
subTitle: Gopal, the son of a generous landlord, disguises himself as an illiterate villager to protect the villagers from the cruel Vijay Bahadur, the brother of his step-mother.

title: Anari
subTitle: Rama, a simpleton, is appointed as the bodyguard of Rajnandini, a rich girl. She soon falls in love with him but her brothers' violent nature gets in the way of her uniting with Rama.

title: Videsh
subTitle: A drug lord escapes from India to Britain, assuming the identity of Swami Prem Babu to continue his illegal activities. When he learns that CBI Inspector Prasad Sinha is investigating him, he kidnaps Sinha's daughter.

title: Nai Imarat
subTitle: Movie starring Parikshit Sahni, Vidya Sinha and directed by Ram Pahlwa, Sharad Batra.

title: Kaamchor
subTitle: An idler falls in love with a rich girl and marries her, wanting to stay with her family. However, to his dismay, she decides to move out, prompting him to demand a share of his father-in-law's wealth.

title: Kal Aaj Aur Kal
subTitle: Ram Bahadur Kapoor faces a dilemma when his son wants to marry for love, but his father insists on arranging the grandson's marriage.

title: Khandan
subTitle: Radha marries a kind-hearted Govind who is paralysed due to an accident. Though Govind highly respects his uncle and aunt, a property dispute forces them to live like strangers under the same roof.

title: Nafrat Ki Aandhi
subTitle: Ravi Kapoor, a police officer and Sonu Dada, a former criminal join hands together to take down a notorious gangster, Chandi Das.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Seema, the daughter of a wealthy businessman, falls in love with a labourer. However, complications arise when Seema's father refuses to accept their relationship.

title: Kabeela
subTitle: Shobha, a poor woman living with her widower father, falls in love with a gypsy named Mangal. However, other men who wish to be with her make her life difficult.

title: Kabeela
subTitle: Shobha, a poor woman living with her widower father, falls in love with a gypsy named Mangal. However, other men who wish to be with her make her life difficult.

title: Khuda Kasam
subTitle: CBI Officer Neetu Singh is framed for the assassination of a chief minister. She then attempts to solve this murder mystery with the help of a man, who is imprisoned for a crime he never committed.

title: Do Phool
subTitle: Fed up with the irresponsible behaviour of his sons, Diwan Bahadur Atal Rai, a wealthy man, decides to disown them. However, chaos erupt when a son claims that he has murdered his brother.

title: Anjaan Raahen
subTitle: Anand who comes from London to India and he employed as teacher in local school. Anand is attracted to Geeta who is also working in the same school, but she doesn't fall in him.

title: Takkar
subTitle: Young Kishan is separated from his family due to the evil intentions of his stepmother and her brother. Years later, he returns under a different identity.

title: Kasme Vaade
subTitle: Raju is guilt-ridden when his involvement with gangsters get his brother, Amit, killed. When he meets Shankar, Amit's lookalike, he decides to make amends, not realising who Shankar really is.

title: Kirayadar
subTitle: When Anil, son of their absentee landlord, arrives in Mumbai and asks them to move out of his home, Laxmi and Jaya's lives turn chaotic.

title: Hero
subTitle: Sooraj, the son of gangster Suryakant Pasha, kidnaps Radha, the daughter of the chief of police. They fall in love after spending some time together but the police and Pasha's men try to catch them.

title: Dushman
subTitle: Surjit Singh, a truck driver, kills a man while driving in the thick fog. However, his life changes when the judge sentences him to serve the victim's family.

title: Kala Dhanda Goray Log
subTitle: Framed for murder by a ruthless drug lord, Gauri Shankar loses everything. Years later, he resurfaces with a new persona and joins forces with a notorious gang to take down his enemies.

title: Kala Dhanda Goray Log
subTitle: Framed for murder by a ruthless drug lord, Gauri Shankar loses everything. Years later, he resurfaces with a new persona and joins forces with a notorious gang to take down his enemies.

title: Phir Wohi Dil Laya Hoon
subTitle: Due to a rift in their relationship, Jamuna leaves her husband and takes her son Mohan with her. Years later, her husband announces that his son has returned, unaware that the man is an imposter.

title: Mausam
subTitle: A medical student nurtures a secret relationship with a woman during his college days. Several years later, he faces a rude shock after finding his illegitimate daughter involved in the flesh trade.

title: Shikar
subTitle: A man is killed when he tries to molest a girl. She absconds with the police on her trail and meets a man who tries to help her find the real murderer.

title: Aap Aye Bahaar Ayee
subTitle: Kumar and Rohit, who are childhood friends, soon turn enemies when Kumar molests Rohit's fiancee out of jealousy. She feels unworthy of Rohit and calls off the wedding.

title: Mother India
subTitle: Radha, a poor but righteous woman, struggles to raise her children opposing Sukhilala, a greedy moneylender. Despite the hurdles, she refuses to sacrifice her integrity.

title: Bobby
subTitle: Raja, the son of a rich Hindu businessman, falls in love with Bobby, a poor Catholic girl. Though their families try to keep them away from each other, they strive to be together.

title: Aadmi Aur Insaan
subTitle: Jai and Munish, fall for the same girl, ruining their bond with each other. However, an unfortunate turn of events reveals the true nature of their friendship.

title: Alag Alag
subTitle: A village belle marries an older doctor for his money, while singer Neeraj moves in with a movie starlet in the hope of getting more work. However, unexpected events occur and change their lives.
